  "stem": "<p>In the <em>xy</em>-plane, the graphs of <math><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced></math> and <math><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math> intersect at two points. Which of the following is one of those points?</p>",
