  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. Setting <math><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math> gives <em>x</em> + 3 = 4 or <em>x</em> + 3 = -4, so <em>x</em> = 1 or <em>x</em> = -7. The point (-7, 4) is an intersection point.</p><p>Choices B, C, and D are incorrect.</p>",
